        <a
          class="text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 flex items-center px-3 py-2.5 no-underline transition-colors"
          href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a
        >
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>	<div class="space-y-12 mt-12">
		<div id="features" class="box bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-white/50 p-6 shadow-lg">
			<h2>How It Works</h2>
			<p>
				1. Tell us what you want to accomplish<br />
