				3. Get it done and keep your money ðŸŽ‰
			</p>
		</div>

		<div id="accountability" class="box bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-white/50 p-6 shadow-lg">
			<h2>Real Accountability</h2>
			<p>We're not just another todo list - we're your accountability partner. By putting a bit of money on the line, you're making a promise to your future self that you intend to keep.</p>
			<p class="mt-4">Completed the task but forgot to check it off? No worries! Just reply to the charge notification and we'll cancel the charge for you.</p>
		</div>

		<div id="integrations" class="box bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-white/50 p-6 shadow-lg">
			<h2>Integrations</h2>
			<p>Seamlessly connects with Beeminder to track your goals.</p>
		</div>

